### Image upload endpoint
# Uploads a single image to Cloudinary and returns its hosted URL.
# The form field name MUST be "file" (matches upload.single("file") on the server).
# Requires the VS Code "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client).

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Upload an image
# Put an image next to this file (e.g. rest/sample.jpg) or change the path after "< ".
# Limits: images only, max 10 MB.
# The response returns: { "url": "...", "publicId": "..." }
# Use that "url" as the "image" value when creating a project (see projects.rest).
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--
